                    <span>this album only deserves one rating 5 stars. What was supposed to be a laid back session of standards has become a timeless classic. Every song on this album is a highpoint. I like bluetrane the best but this one comes in close second along w/ giant steps. Giant Steps may showcase trane's talent more but my fav things shows his timeless class.</span>
                  
              
